 <instruction>hakch das klain</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>tue gehakchtten <ingredient en="bacon" commodity="Q11106">spekch</ingredient> darczu</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>full das <ingredient en="suckling pig" commodity="Q23015">vaerel</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>stekch es an den <tool en="spit" commodity="Q20181361">spizz</tool></instruction>
 <instruction>pratt es sanfft</instruction>
